OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few spots
OL,6,Fof rain possible in Cumbria this
OL,7,Fevening, otherwise a dry night across
OL,8,Fthe region. Some patches of low cloud
OL,9,Fmay form, and staying warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAny low cloud lifting and
OL,12,Fbreaking to give another warm and
OL,13,Fsunny day. A brisk breeze picking up
OL,14,Finto the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,17,FStaying dry, sunny and settled through
OL,18,Fthe outlook and staying very warm.
OL,19,FWinds gradually easing for everyone
OL,20,Fafter the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
